text: Andrey Dmitriyevich Minakov (; born 17 March 2002) is a Russian swimmer. He participated at the 2019 World Aquatics Championships, winning a medal. ==References== Category:2002 births Category:Living people Category:Russian male swimmers Category:Male freestyle swimmers Category:Swimmers at the 2018 Summer Youth Olympics Category:Youth Olympic gold medalists for Russia Category:World Aquatics Championships medalists in swimming Category:Male butterfly swimmers
